      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">No, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I sub 2\"><math alttext=\"I sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span> cannot be determined without knowing the rate at which <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I sub 0\"><math alttext=\"I sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span> is reduced to zero.</p>",
